reviewText: Outstanding bluegrass music! Some great original recordings!

This series of the old time traditional bluegrass music collections mean a lot not only for the bluegrass music lovers like me but also for people who like American roots music. The stories in many songs should teach today's youngsters what the life should mean.
Film part of the production was so well done in addition to music part and it is pure fun to watch and listen and sing alone!!! Just a wonderfully production ever.
I love all Bluegrass and this is all I expected
Too much talking and not enough picking and singing.
interesting talk but to much and short on music
